body_html: There was a bug in TocoConvert.from_keras_model_file in TensorFlow 1.10. It will be fixed in TensorFlow 1.11 (when that is released). For now, as @aselle mentioned, it was fixed in August 9th's nightly build (pip install tf-nightly).

body: There was a bug in `TocoConvert.from_keras_model_file` in TensorFlow 1.10. It will be fixed in TensorFlow 1.11 (when that is released). For now, as @aselle mentioned, it was fixed in August 9th's nightly build (`pip install tf-nightly`).
